* Psuedocode

        totalcost← 0 
        for each v ∈ V
            do MAKE-SET (v)
        sort the edges into non-decreasing order by weight
        for each edge (u, v) ∈ E, taken in non-decreasing order
            do if FIND-SET (u) ≠ FIND-SET (v)
                then UNION (u, v) 
                    totalcost← totalcost+ w(u, v)
        return totalcost

